                            <comment id="440548" author="adilger" created="Thu, 9 Jan 2025 09:37:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would be OK to add a similar check to &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; to check the nodemap name, but this is still needed on the MDS to verify that the (old, broken, bad) client did not pass a bad nodemap name.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="440535" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 9 Jan 2025 03:31:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can we move the function of nodemap_name_is_valid() from the server side to the client side, so that these useful messages can be returned and printed directly ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
